The '''San Jose BioCenter''' is a [[business incubator]] formed as a university foundation in 2004 and focused on the initiation and development of technology companies, with an emphasis on the [[life sciences]] industry.<ref name=rdmagLivingston>{{Citation
 |author=Paul Livingstone |publication-date=February 15, 2012 |title=Hatching Business Success |magazine=[[R&D Magazine]] |at=rdmag.com |volume=54 |issue=1 |url=http://www.rdmag.com/Featured-Articles/2012/02/Policy-And-Industry-Hatching-Business-Success/ |accessdate=September 13, 2012
 }}</ref><ref name=IBSP_SJRA>{{Citation
 |title=Incubators and Business Service Programs |type=website |publisher=[[San Jose Redevelopment Agency]] |url=http://www.sjredevelopment.org/incubators.htm |accessdate=September 13, 2012
 }}</ref>  The BioCenter emerged from [[San Jose State University]] in an effort to revitalize an industrial area of [[San Jose, California]].<ref name=rdmagLivingston/>  {{As of|2012}}, the BioCenter had thirty-five member (assisted) companies and twelve affiliate (supporting) companies.<ref name=rdmagLivingston/><ref name=IBSP_SJRA/>  In addition to office space, the BioCenter provides [[wet laboratory]] facilities to member companies.<ref name=rdmagLivingston/><ref>{{Citation
 |author=Tony Davila |author2=Marc J. Epstein |author3=Robert D. Shelton |year=2007 |title=The Creative Enterprise: Strategy |publisher=[[Greenwood Publishing Group]] (Praeger Publishers) |publication-place=[[Westport, Connecticut]] |page=82 |isbn=9780275986865 |oclc=71350541 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=igqcpDuwkeAC&lpg=PA82&ots=2j4mFydl5X&dq=San%20Jose%20BioCenter&pg=PA82#v=onepage&q=San%20Jose%20BioCenter&f=false |accessdate=September 13, 2012
 }}</ref>

==Awards and recognition==
The BioCenter was awarded in 2009 two "incubator of the year" awards from the [[National Business Incubation Association]].<ref>{{Citation
 |author=Mary Jo Milillo |date=February–March 2010 |title=NBIA Incubator of the Year gives biotechnology clients a "big company advantage" |type=online article summary |work=NBIA Archives |publisher=[[National Business Incubation Association]] |url=http://www.nbia.org/resource_library/review_archive/0210_03a.php |accessdate=September 13, 2012
 }}</ref>

